notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: R.R., G.S., B.C., S.B. conceived and designed research. M.C.E. extracted the EO. G.F., R.A. performed chemical analysis. G.S. and R.R. conducted EAG and morphological investigations. P.F., B.C. and S.B. conducted the behavioral bioassays. S.B., G.S. performed the statistical analyses. R.R., S.B. wrote the manuscript. All authors read and approved the manuscript.
